Program: Discovery
Title: Science in Brazil - cancer
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jry9y
Last Broadcast Date: 04 February 2003
Report on cancer research being carried out in Brazil. First in a three-part series looking at scientific research in Brazil. The nation best-known for its rainforest has huge social and economic problems, yet also has a long-history of scientific research. The programme looks at the breakthroughs in cancer research made in Brazil. Presenter: Julian Siddle. Show less